# Generated API reference (docusaurus-plugin-openapi-docs). Regenerated from
# openapi/airborne.openapi.json on every build/start via the prebuild/prestart
# hooks, so it is not committed — this also avoids secret-scanner false positives
# on the embedded base64 "api:" blob. Only the OpenAPI spec (openapi/) is tracked.
